title: AIDA64 5.70.3800 Portable.zip
description:
About this release

Release date: 22/03/2016
Registration: all 3 versions are registered and automatic updates check is disabled
Usage: unpack your version and run main executable

About AIDA64 5.70

Today FinalWire released an update to the PC editions of its award-winning system information software. Version 5.70 comes with new multi-threaded ray tracing benchmarks, which fully utilize the latest instruction set extensions (AVX, AVX2, FMA). The new floating point tests use more realistic workloads and put more intensive load on the CPU.

- AVX and FMA accelerated FP32 and FP64 ray tracing benchmarks
- Vulkan API information for graphics accelerators
- Improved support for AMD Zen Summit Ridge CPUs
- Sensor support for Corsair AXi power supply units
- Support for Microsoft Windows 10 Redstone RS1 Insider Preview
- Support for Corsair, Logitech, Razer RGB LED mice
